high_descs: Turn to the left and walk forward then turn left again and head to the brown shelves.
Pick up the sponge from the brown shelves.
Turn to the right then turn right again and go across to the counter.
Place the sponge in the pot.
Pick up the sponge and the pot off of the counter
Turn right and then right again and go to the table.
Place the pot and sponge on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a pot and sponge to the table.

high_descs: Turn around, go across the room to face the rack with a sponge and a cleaner
Pick up the sponge from the rack
Turn to your right, move forward a few steps, turn right and go to the counter
Place the sponge in the pot on the counter
Pick up the pot with the sponge from the counter
Go across the room to the table with a pot plant
Put the pot with the sponge on the table
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a sponge on the table

high_descs: Turn left then walk across the room head to the shelf rack
Pick up the sponge on the shelf rack
Turn right then cross the room head to the counter on your left
Put the sponge in the pot
Pick up the pot with sponge
Turn right then walk forward head to the round table
Put the pot with sponge on the left side of the round table
anns.task_desc: Put the pot with sponge on the left side of the round table
